Package aso.model

Class WeatherData

  • java.lang.Object
    • aso.model.WeatherData

  • public class WeatherData
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that manages the lowest level of the data model. One instance of the WeatherData class corresponds to one line in a csv containing weather data for a station and month.

        rainFall - Total recorded rainfall
